configuration options it can get sensible defaults by doing any of the following:\n+ * Not sending `initializationOptions`\n+ * Send `\"initializationOptions\": null`\n+ * Send `\"initializationOptions\": {}`\n \n ## Snippet `TextEdit`\n "}]}